results.title: Polymer Clay Milk Pitcher and Chocolate Chip Cookie, 'Live, Laugh, Love' Silver Charm, Silver Filigree Diamond Shaped Charm, Gold Swarovski
results.description:
All you really need to do is Live, Laugh, Love and have a little bit of milk and Cookies!

This car mirror or home hanging charm measures approximately 5.5 inches (140 mm) in length from the top of the open jump ring at the end of the flexible snake chain extender to the bottom curve of the polymer clay milk pitcher. The silver chain, that attaches the charm to the rear-view car mirror or to that special hook in your home or office, measures 10 in (254 mm), 5 inches (127 mm) doubled. This piece can be customized for size by changing the lobster clasp placement on the chain or by double wrapping the chain, giving you options when hanging this special piece. 

From a silver filigree diamond shaped Charm (51 mm x 32 mm), there are four silver finish chains presenting the following: 

*The top chain, hanging from the top of the diamond-shaped charm, holds an important message ...' live, laugh, love' proclaimed on a silver round charm (20 mm)…with the reverse side detailed in spiral relief engravings. 

*The middle silver chain hangs down front and centre near the bottom portion of the diamond-shaped charm which shows well the hand sculptured green polymer clay milk pitcher measuring approximately 1" x 1" x .75" (25 mm x 25 mm x 13mm ). The milk pitcher has a healthy stream of milk-white clay overflowing over the pitcher's narrow top curve, with some of the milk lightly staining the front of the pitcher; its handle is a curved silver grip with the sides hand-painted with acrylic paint depicting the blue and green of wildflowers you might spot out a country kitchen window. 

*Hanging close to the cool milk pitcher is the chain holding the very important, the very tasty looking, Polymer Clay Chocolate Chip Cookie (19 mm x 25 mm). The cookie has been hand sculpted on both sides with plenty of dark chocolate chips peeking through to entice you further. 

* The remaining chain offers up two golden, cookie coloured 6mm Swarovksi crystals, the two crystals separated by a small silver spacer and artfully wire wrapped to the chain. The crystals add perfectly to the colour and promise of a little taste of a Chocolate Chip Cookie. 

(25 mm = 2.5 cm = 1 inch)

Here is a wonderful gift of comfort!

                                                “Reach as high as you can,
                                                  then reach a little higher.
                                                 There, you will find magic and possibility.
                                                  And maybe even cookies”
